Market News  11 PM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-Discover Financial Services Credit Card Delinquency Rate 1.80 Pct At March End Vs 1.84 Pct At February End Reuters Staff 
April 16 (Reuters) - Discover Financial Services: 
* CREDIT CARD DELINQUENCY RATE 1.80 PERCENT AT MARCH END VERSUS 1.84 PERCENT AT FEBRUARY END 
* CREDIT CARD CHARGE-OFF RATE 2.50 PERCENT AT MARCH END VERSUS 2.19 PERCENT AT FEBRUARY END - SEC FILING Source text:( bit.ly/2H2uVdt ) Further company coverage:
